---
// Override of Starlight's ThemeProvider. The docs are light-only (they
// match the light-first app), so instead of reading localStorage /
// `prefers-color-scheme`, we pin `data-theme="light"`. Inline + in
// <head> so it lands before first paint — no flash of the default
// dark theme.
---

<script is:inline>
	document.documentElement.dataset.theme = 'light'
</script>
